PortSystem 1.0
name		gnome-icon-theme
version		1.0.6
description	A collection of icons for the GNOME 2 desktop.
long_description        gnome-icon-theme is a collection of icons and \
			emblems for the GNOME 2 desktop.
maintainers	olegb@opendarwin.org
categories	gnome
platforms	darwin 
homepage	http://www.gnome.org/
master_sites    ftp://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/desktop/2.2/2.2.2/sources/
checksums	md5 1d5b1e77fda701950b8b86f6444426c1
